    {
      "id": 10912,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "@zhurig found a race condition where it was possible to bypass the limit for the number of locations a store can have by submitting multiple requests at once. We have resolved this issue by adding extra transactional locking during store location changes.\n\n**Note**: Shopify no longer accepts reports regarding race conditions bypassing plan limits to this bug bounty program. Please make sure to check that your report has additional merchant impact beyond bypassing a plan limit before reporting.",
